Power BI Report Output – Internship Task 2: Data Integration

🧷 Data Sources Used
🔵 SQL Server – WalmartSalesDB

Table: Sales

Fields: OrderID, StoreID, ProductID, SalesAmount, Date, Quantity

🟢 Excel File – products.xlsx

Table: Products

Fields: ProductID, ProductName, Category, Price

🔁 Data Model (Relationships)
Sales.ProductID → Products.ProductID

One-to-Many Relationship from Products to Sales

📊 Visuals Created
1. 📈 Sales Trend Over Time
Visual: Line Chart

X-Axis: Date

Y-Axis: Total SalesAmount

Slicer: Product Category

2. 💰 Total Sales by Category
Visual: Column Chart

Axis: Category

Values: SUM of SalesAmount

3. 🛍️ Top 10 Products by Sales
Visual: Bar Chart

Axis: ProductName

Values: Total SalesAmount

Filtered: Top 10

4. 📍 Sales by Store Location
Visual: Map (if location data is available)

Values: Total SalesAmount

Location: Store/City

5. 🧾 Sales Summary Table
Visual: Table

Fields: OrderID, ProductName, Quantity, SalesAmount, Date

6. 📦 KPI Cards
Total Sales

Total Quantity Sold

Average Sales per Order

